---
title: Honey-Soy Pork Bunless Burger with Creamy Slaw
description: Here’s a fun idea for tonight’s dinner, burgers without the buns! Not convinced yet, well let’s fix that. These pork patties are cooked in a delicious teriyaki sauce after being combined with both ginger and garlic, with a side of roast veggies sprinkled with sesame seeds. Without a bun, all these flavours shine in the bowl. So what do you think, isn’t this the best kind of burger option you’ve ever had!

